#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:12
msgid "Tools"
msgstr "ツール"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:12
msgid "Polygon"
msgstr "多角形"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:12
msgid "Selection"
msgstr "選択"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:12
msgid "Polygonal Selection"
msgstr "多角形選択"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:17
msgid "Polygonal Selection Tool"
msgstr "多角形選択ツール"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:19
msgid "|toolselectpolygon|"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:21
msgid ""
"This tool, represented by a polygon with a dashed border, allows you to "
"make :ref:`selections_basics` in a polygonal shape. To make a polygonal "
"selection |mouseleft| and place points or nodes of the polygon. To finalize "
"your selection area you can do either |mouseleft| on the first created "
"point, or double |mouseleft| click to end the polygon."
msgstr ""
"破線の多角形で表されるこのツールは、多角形の :ref:`selections_basics` を作成"
"することができます。多角形選択を作成するには |mouseleft| で角や線を置いていき"
"ます。最後に選択を確定したい場合は最初の点に |mouseleft| するか、|mouseleft| "
"ダブルクリックで完成させます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:25
msgid ""
"Most of the behavior of the Polygonal Selection Tool is common to all other "
"selection tools, please make sure to read :ref:`selections_basics` to learn "
"more about this tool."
msgstr ""
"多角性選択ツールのほとんどの機能は他の選択ツールと共通ですので、より詳しく"
"は :ref:`selections_basics` を見てください。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:30
msgid "Hotkeys and Sticky keys"
msgstr "ホットキーとスティッキーキー"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:32
msgid ""
":kbd:`Shift +` |mouseleft| temporarily sets the subsequent selection to "
"'add' mode. Release the :kbd:`Shift` key will return to the current "
"permanent mode. Same for the others."
msgstr ""
":kbd:`Shift +` |mouseleft| で一時的に次される選択を'加算'モードにしま"
"す。:kbd:`Shift` キーを離すと現在設定されたモードに戻ります。他も同様です。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:33
msgid ""
":kbd:`Alt +` |mouseleft| temporarily sets the subsequent selection to "
"'subtract' mode."
msgstr ""
":kbd:`Alt +` |mouseleft| で一時的に次される選択を'除外'モードにします。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:34
msgid ""
":kbd:`Ctrl +` |mouseleft| temporarily sets the subsequent selection to "
"'replace' mode."
msgstr ":kbd:`Ctrl +` |mouseleft| で一時的に次される選択に'置換'します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:35
msgid ""
":kbd:`Shift + Alt +` |mouseleft| temporarily sets the subsequent selection "
"to 'intersect' mode."
msgstr ""
":kbd:`Shift + Alt +` |mouseleft| で次される選択との'積集合'を取ります。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:39
msgid ""
"Hovering your cursor over the dashed line of the selection, or marching ants "
"as it is commonly called, turns the cursor into the move tool icon, which "
"you |mouseleft| and drag to move the selection."
msgstr ""
"選択の破線にマウスホバーすることで、カーソルが移動ツールアイコンに代わり、|"
"mouseleft| でドラッグすることで選択を移動できます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:40
msgid ""
"|mouseright| will open up a selection quick menu with amongst others the "
"ability to edit the selection."
msgstr ""
"|mouseright| で他の選択編集機能にアクセスできる選択クイックメニューが開きま"
"す。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:44
msgid ""
"If you already began making a selection, |mouseright| will undo the last "
"added point."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:52
msgid ""
"You can switch the behavior of the :kbd:`Alt` key to use :kbd:`Ctrl` key "
"instead by toggling the switch in Tool Settings in "
"the :ref:`general_settings`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`general_settings` にあるツール設定から :kbd:`Alt` キーと :kbd:`Ctrl` "
"キーの振る舞いを入れ替えることができます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:56
msgid ""
"This tool is not bound to any Hotkey, if you want to define one, go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Configure Krita --> Keyboard Shortcuts` and "
"search for 'Polygonal Selection Tool', there you can select the shortcut you "
"want. Check :ref:`shortcut_settings` for more info."
msgstr ""
"このツールはどのホットキーにも関連付けられていませんので、定義したい場合"
"は、:menuselection:`設定 --> Krita の設定を変更 --> キーボードショートカット"
"` に行き、'多角形選択ツール'で設定したいショートカットを選択できます。詳しく"
"は :ref:`shortcut_settings` を見てください。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:60
msgid "Tool Options"
msgstr "ツールのオプション"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:66
msgid "Mode"
msgstr "モード"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:67
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:69
msgid "This option is explained in the :ref:`pixel_vector_selection` section."
msgstr ""
"このオプションは :ref:`pixel_vector_selection` の項目で説明しています。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:68
msgid "Action"
msgstr "動作"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:71
msgid "Anti-aliasing"
msgstr "アンチエイリアス"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:71
msgid ""
"This toggles whether or not to give selections feathered edges. Some people "
"prefer hard-jagged edges for their selections."
msgstr ""
"選択のふちを柔らかくすることができます。ジャギーのある硬いふちを好む人もいま"
"す。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:75
msgid "Anti-aliasing is only available on Pixel Selection Mode."
msgstr "アンチエイリアスはピクセル選択モードでのみ使用可能です。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/polygonal_select.rst:-1
msgid "Krita's polygonal selection tool reference."
msgstr "Krita 多角形選択ツールの説明。"

